OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells and the odd shower at
OL,7,Ffirst, then becoming cloudier
OL,8,Fovernight with showers becoming more
OL,9,Ffrequent and heavier at times. Rather
OL,10,Fbreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy in the morning
OL,13,Fwith scattered showers, heavy at
OL,14,Ftimes. Becoming dry through the
OL,15,Fafternoon with some bright spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping. Breezy at times,
OL,17,Fespecially around the Antrim coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
