OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry on
OL,6,FSunday with some brightness. Dry and
OL,7,Fbright start on Monday but turning
OL,8,Fcloudier later. Variable cloud and
OL,9,Fbright spells on Tuesday with some
OL,10,Fshowers, rain later. Becoming warmer.
